window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>A debt is owed...and time is running out! </b></p> <p>Ayrion’s tribe has until the Harvest Moon to meet the Guild’s price. If the payment isn’t made, Hurricane’s territory will be seized, and its members left to starve. </p> <p>The stakes have never been higher. </p> <p>Once again, Ayrion finds himself in the precarious position of taking on the role of savior. Only this time, it’s not just his life that hangs in the balance, but the lives of all the children he protects.</p> <p>Desperation can lead people to attempt the impossible, but Ayrion has truly tipped the scales on this one.</p>"; 
